<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Mahogany</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The community is bounded by the Stoney Trail on the north the East Freeway on the east, 196 Avenue SE on the south and the 52 Street SE on the west.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Tucked away within a quiet and scenic suburban area of the city of Calgary in Alberta, Mahogany is home to some of the hottest properties on the real estate market.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Developed by the Hopewell Residential Communities, the Mahogany Real Estate boasts of some of the biggest names in the construction business including the Stepper Homes, Sabal, Jayman and Trico Homes.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">There is a huge variation in the prices of residential units in this area with some of them being priced as low as $200,000 and the figures climbing higher up to five million as well! The 74 acres of natural wetlands and the 13-acre park in the community offer ample recreational opportunities to the residents.</p>

